description.en:
What is the project about?
Reunit is a wallet built on top of LayerZero & Stargate Finance

What makes your project unique?
Reunit allow users to transfer tokens from multiple blockchain to another in a single click

History of your project.
March 2022 : Project started
28 Feb 2023 : Private presale
15 March 2023  : Beta phase one

What’s next for your project?
April 2023 : Beta phase two
May 2023 : Official launch

What can your token be used for?
REUNI is an omnichain token = you can natively transfer it to others chains
